'''Mostafa Ahmed Abdelaziz Mohamed Shobeir''' ({{langx|ar|مصطفي أحمد عبد العزيز محمد شوبير}}; born 15 May 2000) is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for Egyptian club [[Al Ahly SC]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].

== International career ==

On 2 December 2025, Shobeir was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

== Personal life ==
Shobeir is the son of former Egyptian national team goalkeeper [[Ahmed Shobair]].

